description:
Ankahee aka The Unspoken (1985) is a rare film from the Indian parallel cinema era of the 70s &amp; 80s which produced a lot of cinematic gems. It stars two of the most significant- &amp; also my favorite- actors of that era - Amol Palekar &amp; Deepti Naval. The film is directed by Palekar himself. 
