Pandit Satyanarayan Chaturvedi is a renowned astrologer who lives with his wife, Devki, and his only son, Nandu. Nandu is in  love with Sushma &amp; wants to marry her but then his father tells him that his wife will die within an year of the marriage. Nandu is now in a dilemma &amp; must decide to believe his father and let go of Sushma, or defy his astrological beliefs and marry her.


